        {
            "title": "A股滬股重上3800關 創板升逾6.5%  一周累計滬深俱跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股午後升勢進一步擴大，滬股重上3800以上，深股升近4%，創板升6.55%，全日成交23046.59億元 (人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230629_FI_A-SHARE_5_source-ap_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230629_FI_A-SHARE_5_source-ap_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指全日收升46點或1.24%，報3812點，今早開報3761點，平開，最低見3745點，跌20點或0.53%，即反覆向上，午後破上午高位，見3817點，升52點或1.38%，為全日高位，全日成交9790.62億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">一周累計跌45點或1.18%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指全日升471或3.89%，報12590，今早開報12140，升22點或0.18%，早段低見12085，跌33點或0.27%，午後高見12597，揚479點或3.95%，全日成交13255.97億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">一周累計跌106點或0.83%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300全日升95點或2.18%，報4460點，今早開報4365，平開。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數全日升181點或6.55%，報2958點，今早開報2793，升17點或0.54%。</p>\n</div>",
